videos.description: Maryland gets an easy bucket in the first half against Purdue thanks to some quick cuts.

videos.headline: Bender finds slashing Trimble for bucket

videos.description: Dakota Mathias denies Maryland on the fastbreak
videos.headline: Great D by Dakota Mathias snuffs out the Maryland break

videos.headline: Trimble and Cekovsky connect on the alley-oop

videos.description: Melo Trimble slices through the Boilermakers defense and finishes with contact.

Michal Cekovsky with four blocks in the first half

videos.description: Maryland forces a Purdue timeout in the second half with this big-time play.

videos.description: Designed play for M. Cekovsky who moves off the ball and cuts to the basket, where  Cowan finds him for the opop.
videos.headline: Cowan finds the cutting Cekovsky for the alley-oop

videos.description: Caleb Swanigan keeps the play alive, delivers the perfect tap to Thompson to give Purdue the lead.
videos.headline: Swanigan tap-out to Thompson gives Purdue the lead

videos.description: C. Swanigan made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by D. Mathias.
videos.headline: Swanigan three pulls Boilermakers within one
Terrapins bail Boilermakers out, send Edwards to line with chance to take lead

videos.description: Edwards free throw gives Purdue lead, the Maryland in-bounds pass is picked off by Haas who walks with it, giving Maryland one more shot.
videos.headline: Purdue picks off late desperate pass, but turns it over

videos.description: K. Huerter gets an open look but can convert the three to win the game.
videos.headline: Kevin Huerter misses game-winning three-point attempt
